description:
We have many bots here!

:small_blue_diamond: <@235148962103951360>
This one does most of the background work, you'll see them most when someone joins. Can be used nearly everywhere but don't spam!

:small_blue_diamond: <@172002275412279296>
Used to have a bigger presence, but not so much now.  Also has a few games. Keep use to <#398191639488757770>.

:small_blue_diamond: <@185476724627210241>
She is the student’s pet and also can post images on command. Do not spam her commands unless it is in a designated spam channel or #bots  although an occasional hug or pat is appreciated and allowed in general.

:small_blue_diamond: <@235088799074484224>
Plays music. Time to listen to My Soul, Your Beats for the next hour.

:small_blue_diamond: <@289066747443675143>
Used for <#472913118796709888> to do osu things.

:small_blue_diamond: <@700754901549973645>
Made by <@264612287048843264>. This bot is the Council’s pet and posts images or gifs, as well as a few small pastimes shipping people! Refrain from spamming unless in <#398191639488757770>. Also aids in some server operations.

:small_blue_diamond: <@534589798267224065>
As you guessed it this bot is used to keep track of your rank and upvote or downvote other students. Remember to keep use in #bots and keep those Grades up!
title: The NPCs that live here
